doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Tasker Privacy Policy
    style
      include ./static/tasker.css
  body
    header
      h1 Tasker Privacy Policy
      p Effective Date: 18-12-2023
    main
      p
        | Thank you for choosing Tasker! This Privacy Policy outlines the information practices for Tasker ("we," "us," or "our") regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information when you use our mobile application (the "App").
      section
        h2 Information We Collect
        p
          | Tasker only accesses the camera and gallery on your device. We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal information from these sources.
      section
        h2 How We Use Your Information
        p
          | Tasker utilizes camera and gallery access solely for the purpose of enabling you to capture and process images for further processes. We do not use this information for any other purpose, and we do not store any images or videos.
      section
        h2 No Data Storage
        p
          | Tasker does not store any personal data, images, or videos on our servers or any external storage. All data remains on your device, and Tasker does not have access to or control over the content stored on your device.
      section
        h2 Permissions
        p
          | Tasker requires camera and gallery access permissions to function properly. You can manage app permissions in your device settings.
      section
        h2 Security
        p
          | We take the security of your data seriously. Tasker employs industry-standard measures to protect the information accessed through the camera and gallery on your device. However, since no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, we cannot guarantee absolute security.
      section
        h2 Changes to This Privacy Policy
        p
          | We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon the posting of the revised Privacy Policy. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.
      section
        h2 Consent
        p
          | By using Tasker, you consent to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
    footer
      p This privacy policy was last updated on December 18, 2023.
